of Chen Ying’s party...)

636
00:30:38,060 --> 00:30:38,780
(Xiao Heng escaped luckily...)

637
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:46,510
Mother.

638
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:51,790
Banxia.

639
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:53,910
Guard the door.

640
00:30:54,190 --> 00:30:56,430
