651
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:23,120
My men are still hunting him.

652
00:31:24,190 --> 00:31:26,120
These are what he has left behind

653
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:28,150
in a sealed chamber at Rugui House.

654
00:31:28,710 --> 00:31:30,600
