665
00:31:57,650 --> 00:32:00,600
I invited Madam Jing.

666
00:32:01,230 --> 00:32:02,790
Someone is spying on us.

667
00:32:04,190 --> 00:32:05,120
So, I didn’t allow Wu Jiang to

668
00:32:05,230 --> 00:32:07,270
