murdered by Chen Ying.

739
00:34:57,970 --> 00:34:59,090
When I led Shence Army
to suppress the rebellion

740
00:34:59,110 --> 00:35:01,890
at His Majesty’s behest.

741
00:35:01,890 --> 00:35:03,330
