00:36:55,620 --> 00:36:57,690
♪Nothing can♪

772
00:36:59,010 --> 00:37:01,290
♪Stop me♪

773
00:37:02,650 --> 00:37:04,450
♪From missing you♪

774
00:37:04,690 --> 00:37:08,450
♪All the time♪

